From 06c2624491a79673149a99d5c597bd0ff388c867 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Ram Mohan M <ram.mohan@ittiam.com>
Date: Sat, 18 May 2024 21:21:12 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] Updates to jpeg decoder helper util class

jpegdecoderutil class handles subsampling format 420. Decoding images
with other sub sampling formats return with error. This class is now
updated to handle various 4:a:b configurations

removed possible oob access in parse xmp metadata

fixed warnings in sample app

Test: ./ultrahdr_unit_test
Test: ./ultrahdr_dec_fuzzer
